## Summary

This documentation covers the Amplitude Experiment JavaScript SDK for client-side feature flag evaluation, including installation via npm/yarn/script, initialization methods (standalone, Unified SDK, third-party analytics), remote and local evaluation with fetch/start methods, variant access with automatic exposure tracking, and integrations with Amplitude Analytics, Segment, and mParticle.

